comments.body:
Hello

We couldn't reproduce this issue. App runs successfully on iOS 9 device in our testing environment. If you still run into this error, let us know the details steps you take to publish app and environment details.

*Testing Environment:*
Appcelerator Studio, build: 5.1.0.201508271018
Xcode version : 7.0
Mac OSX : 10.10.5
device version : iOS 9
Node.js Version : 0.10.37
npm Version      : 1.4.28
Titanium CLI	   : 5.0.5
Ti SDK Version : 5.0.2.GA

*Steps to test:*
Create a simple app, build and deploy on iOS 9 device.

Thanks.
